{"tid":1449672,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T19:10:03.000Z","uid":137802,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"3086b83ae00c610dbc97405f6f60eec51372a60f","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:00:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不論你係和理非定勇武<br />\n希望大家都會入機場<br />\n</span></span><br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n不沖禁區，不沖跑道<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停<br />\n百萬人入機場，機場自然停"},{"pid":"d7da306d4dd4d17c76284245ef9bb3e32157e663","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:14.000Z","msg":"自推10次"},{"pid":"716309cc1213fc7f39012b90e6a7fbde99a4c52f","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"aeb66c8e688e988baa23323eeff0dbda58ca7219","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:34.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"9f8d526ba0b0630cd8c2efd3b43e2ee798b91355","tid":1449672,"uid":92476,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"幫推 <br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">內有機場抗爭論述，策略及方案</span><br />\n請以機場抗爭方向作主軸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1445387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1445387</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">該post 以和理非手段解決<br />\n兄弟爬山 其他人有其他方式抗爭 請自行決定 會尊重及諒解 不用互相攻擊 各有各做</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n機場七小隊分為：星期一小隊，星期二小隊⋯⋯星期日小隊，二百萬人除365日，可以每人每日輪流五千人，不用衝禁區，全年365日申請集會<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好以兩三日政府冷處理就當睇唔到成效，得兩三日當然唔會對政府有太大影響，但問題持續下去一年半載，政府無得唔處理。</span>"},{"pid":"b4d46a2e8439073d7a2ee72a03120059a6d22ef3","tid":1449672,"uid":298061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"Pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e08b65c9f9f00c4e5fd2d19c1cf7fba8bec5b9","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:44.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"aff5c324ec70af603f04788dc14f01cf8922fe06","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:56.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"96aaffe36665e9c73ace1acdc161f384ed879957","tid":1449672,"uid":266510,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PxfQraE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPxfQraE.png&h=49591f75&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b383cf80bdc853bbb3c4676934268db04f4217e4","tid":1449672,"uid":229296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">警犬扮前線示威者</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">光明正大勾結黑社會</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">地鐵站內放催淚彈</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">布袋彈射爆示威者眼球</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">通街亂拉街坊同路人</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">公安/武警冒充港警</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">全民譴責721</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effe00945d2a9e13bb09ce1faef205abcea6c541","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:06.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"8a691540b1d7ecb0aadd75b858ab6ebf68873384","tid":1449672,"uid":279111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"［緊急］ 我呼籲 全民blackbloc！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1449581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1449581</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d4c7d2368d79232a2c05f862b53b2ebc9d48999d","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:17.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"908bb77ece9a340819044d11ec167d9d51bc7ad8","tid":1449672,"uid":174541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:21.000Z","msg":"地做開marketing，寫埋本教科書教你跟住做文宣! 成個月咩進步都冇，重係散修修同溫層自high咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記撚住啊!有啲仆街聽到義士爆眼係會拍手叫好。我地再賣血賣肉都喚唔醒班仆街架！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">憤怒過後要冷靜面對</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣嘅諗清楚我地係target緊咩人，要點遊說!</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">前線嘅諗清楚每個行為背後有咩用！淨低嘅交俾我地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n【藍絲攻略 - 拆解 18 種建制】- 徐緣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179283162169650/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F347912661973385%2Fposts%2F2179283162169650%2F&d=WSAeeZJF6zK6RlDtvYZcpk2FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=4207f43d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/347912661973385/posts/2179283162169650/</a>"},{"pid":"8632943de4046e77deb2a63f378ef55a9f097fbb","tid":1449672,"uid":243984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:24.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"e9623065a2d00d331ec6478fb147abeb78cd7d65","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:27.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"9706f8f3215e2c7b24c2b654f84f87e29f283e5c","tid":1449672,"uid":15237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"0113adc21dba3f8e0a44c8284370a379e81320ce","tid":1449672,"uid":251965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:36.000Z","msg":"721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 警方沒有依安全指引直接向示威者頭部水平發射催淚彈/布袋彈/海綿彈等高殺傷力武器<br />\n2. 721在有足夠證據下沒有一位施襲者被起訴<br />\n3. 警方偽裝成示威者在現代帶領並煽動進行違法行為<br />\n4. 濫捕市民<br />\n5. 在密閉空間使用催淚彈，毒素不能散去令其他市民有機會吸入體內<br />\n6. 警方使用不必要武力<br />\n7. 警方執行警權時沒有配戴委任證<br />\n8. 警方使用有毒之過期催淚彈<br />\n9. 警方包庇黑社會向市民施襲<br />\n10. 警方無差別濫捕市民"},{"pid":"9045b7116e47774a9380acf82d2362400d29d1a1","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:39.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"28d452c44c88f9033375eb75bdcb79f4362c0898","tid":1449672,"uid":148152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:44.000Z","msg":"標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場"},{"pid":"16026f0d5ce5018a9fc636261eeec2f0a0dbacbf","tid":1449672,"uid":133019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:48.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23983c47fb5924f5cdec063238d5d389ce007fe","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:03:50.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3bf473440c8d3b09ed98ffc34baf5716677bda6a","tid":1449672,"uid":137802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,